snippet.textDisplay: Honestly as someone who doesn’t like Eminem Dax doesn’t need a collab. Sure it would be great for Dax, but em is so over rated. His fan base can’t even agree on what’s his best time period. Everyone acts like he’s always made gems but his early stuff that everyone raves about wasn’t that great, his latest stuff isn’t that great either and I firmly believe there are rappers that have just as good flow, better voices that sound more lyrical, and almost as good wordplay. Like he isn’t a god y’all. Like he’s just a dude and everyone acts like he’s infallible but he’s made a few really bad albums. Too many act like nobody will be better than Eminem, but rap is young and I think there are people who rapped about more meaningful things before him.
